The Best of Brodie Lee in CZW: 

Brodie Lee, now known as Luke Harper of the Wyatt Family in the WWE, 
was a force to reckon with on the independent wrestling circuit.  
After causing waves Brodie Lee eventually made his way to CZW and left 
a trail of debris behind him.  Thanks to this new addition to our 
Best of CZW series you can now see every Brodie Lee match from the 
Combat Zone in full! 


- Brodie Lee & Cheech vs. Jon Dahmer & GQ

  VS CS2 (J-Busta & Dave Cole)

  Team AnDrew & Nate Hatred
